FBIS4-42621 "drweu109_a_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-109 Daily Report 4 Jun 1994 AUSTRIA Bulgaria's Matchinev Praises Social System Bulgaria's Matchinev Praises Social System AU0506171394 Vienna WIENER ZEITUNG in German 4 Jun 94 p 2 AU0506171394 Vienna WIENER ZEITUNG German BFN [Unattributed report: "Bulgarian-Austrian Rapprochement"] [Text] During a meeting in Vienna between Labor Minister Josef Hesoun and Evgeni Kirilov Matinchev, the deputy prime minister and labor minister, a new chapter in Austrian-Bulgarian relations was opened. "Austria has a good and modern social system. We gladly want to use Austria's experiences in social politics as a model," the Bulgarian deputy prime minister stated after the meeting, according to the Social Ministry's press release. Hesoun promised Bulgaria full support and proposed that a team of Bulgarian experts will aquaint themselves with the social system in Austria.
